Question: Many universities require that freshman live on campus dorm during the first year of college. In your opinion, is this a good or a bad thing? Explain your opinion on this issue.
Answer:
it is acceptable. the dorm life is a necessary part of one's college life. living in dorm helps the freshman build friendship. and also dorms are usually quite close to the classroom, which saves the time. in addition, a dorm is usually furnitured, which is important for new students.